sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor NV as Nhan vien
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant OrderDB as Order DB
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant Customer as Customer Service
    participant CustomerDB as Customer DB

    NV->>GW: PUT /api/orders/:orderId/status
    Note over NV,GW: newStatus=COMPLETED
    GW->>Order: Forward request - yeu cau auth STAFF

    Order->>OrderDB: order.findById(orderId)
    OrderDB-->>Order: order record - status=READY

    Order->>Order: validateStatusTransition - READY -> COMPLETED
    Order->>OrderDB: order.update - status=COMPLETED
    Order->>OrderDB: statusLog.create - changed_by=staffId
    OrderDB-->>Order: order da cap nhat

    alt Don hang co customerId
        Order->>MQ: Publish order_exchange / order.completed
        Note over Order,MQ: customerId, orderId<br/>totalAmount, orderCode
    end

    Order-->>GW: 200 OK - status=COMPLETED
    GW-->>NV: Don hang hoan thanh

    Note over MQ,CustomerDB: Xu ly bat dong bo - Customer Service consume

    MQ->>Customer: Consume order_exchange / order.completed
    Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.findByAccountId(customerId)
    CustomerDB-->>Customer: customer record

    alt Khach hang ton tai
        Customer->>Customer: pointsEarned = floor(totalAmount / 10000)
        Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.update - loyaltyPoints += pointsEarned
        Customer->>CustomerDB: pointLog.create
        Note over Customer,CustomerDB: points, reason=ORDER_COMPLETED<br/>orderId, totalAmount

        alt loyaltyPoints >= 200 va tier = REGULAR
            Customer->>CustomerDB: customer.update - tier=VIP
            Note over Customer: Tu dong nang cap len VIP
        end
    end

